    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>2024 年，浏阳的最后一场烟火秀</p><span id="more"></span><a class="tag-plugin colorful hashtag" color="red" href="/tags/生活"><svg t="1701408144765" class="icon" viewBox="0 0 1024 1024" version="1.1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" p-id="4228" width="200" height="200"><path d="M426.6 64.8c34.8 5.8 58.4 38.8 52.6 73.6l-19.6 117.6h190.2l23-138.6c5.8-34.8 38.8-58.4 73.6-52.6s58.4 38.8 52.6 73.6l-19.4 117.6H896c35.4 0 64 28.6 64 64s-28.6 64-64 64h-137.8l-42.6 256H832c35.4 0 64 28.6 64 64s-28.6 64-64 64h-137.8l-23 138.6c-5.8 34.8-38.8 58.4-73.6 52.6s-58.4-38.8-52.6-73.6l19.6-117.4h-190.4l-23 138.6c-5.8 34.8-38.8 58.4-73.6 52.6s-58.4-38.8-52.6-73.6l19.4-117.8H128c-35.4 0-64-28.6-64-64s28.6-64 64-64h137.8l42.6-256H192c-35.4 0-64-28.6-64-64s28.6-64 64-64h137.8l23-138.6c5.8-34.8 38.8-58.4 73.6-52.6z m11.6 319.2l-42.6 256h190.2l42.6-256h-190.2z" p-id="4229"></path></svg><span>生活</span></a><p>突然发现浏阳家里小区是个看烟花的好场景（下次得到隔壁一栋去看，没有遮挡），带着琦琦和岳母到楼顶欣赏了今年在天空剧院最的最后一场烟火秀，顺便操练了一下相机📷</p><div class="tag-plugin gallery grid-box" size="mix" ratio="square"><div class="grid-cell"><img data-fancybox="gallery-1" src="https://snowinlu.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/DSC_0413.JPG" alt="七彩祥云"/><div class="image-meta"><span class="image-caption">七彩祥云</span></div></div><div class="grid-cell"><img data-fancybox="gallery-1" src="https://snowinlu.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/DSC_0455.JPG" alt="蓝色烟火 01"/><div class="image-meta"><span class="image-caption">蓝色烟火 01</span></div></div><div class="grid-cell"><img data-fancybox="gallery-1" src="https://snowinlu.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/DSC_0450.JPG" alt="蓝色烟火 02"/><div class="image-meta"><span class="image-caption">蓝色烟火 02</span></div></div><div class="grid-cell"><img data-fancybox="gallery-1" src="https://snowinlu.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/DSC_0461.JPG" alt="白色烟火"/><div class="image-meta"><span class="image-caption">白色烟火</span></div></div><div class="grid-cell"><img data-fancybox="gallery-1" src="https://snowinlu.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.